Boxing great Muhummad Ali has won his bout with a severe urinary tract infection.

The three-time world heavyweight champion was released from a hospital Tuesday night, family spokesman Bob Gunnell said Wednesday.

Ali is back home and looking forward to celebrating his 73rd birthday on January 17 with his family and friends, Gunnell said.

